parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shudder or vibration can cause uneven acceleration, loss of power, and decreased vehicle control, which can lead to accidents or affect the overall driving experience.
symptoms: The transmission shakes or vibrates when starting to drive
the vehicle hesitates or lags when accelerating
the transmission makes unusual noises or clunking sounds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving, which can affect the driver's attention and reaction time.
symptoms: The air conditioning unit stops blowing cold air intermittently
the air conditioning unit blows warm or lukewarm air
the air conditioning unit makes unusual noises or smells.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult or impossible to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the transmission temperature gauge rises quickly
the check engine warning light is illuminated
the transmission is leaking
the vehicle is not drivable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission cooling line can cause the transmission to overheat, leading to premature wear and failure, which can cause the vehicle to lose power and become undrivable.
symptoms: The transmission temperature gauge rises quickly
the transmission is leaking
the vehicle is not drivable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defective headlight seals can cause corrosion on the main light board due to humidity, leading to sudden failure of the headlights, which can compromise road safety and visibility.
symptoms: Headlights suddenly stop working
corrosion on the main light board
water or moisture inside the headlight assembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning navigation screen system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and also affect the signal lights, which can compromise road safety.
symptoms: Navigation screen flickers
navigation screen goes completely black
navigation screen turns on and off
signal lights are affected
USB port under the armrest is excessively hot.
